Description: This package provides cleaned ERA5-derived Fire Weather Index (FWI)
    and MODIS burned area summaries for southeastern Australia. It includes a
    Shiny app for interactive exploration of how fire risk (FWI) relates to
    burned area, and a vignette documenting the data processing steps used in
    previous ETC5523 assignments.
